{"tid":1289232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【昔日往聞】林奠：唔知便利店冇廁紙賣","createTime":"2019-07-06T04:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T04:45:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3991eeb0489b41481d3ed63db0de79d0b221594f","tid":1289232,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】繼不懂在港鐵使用八達通入閘後，林鄭月娥再有「堅離地」事件。她昨稱已搬離政務司司長官邸，入住灣仔會景閣，但前晚午夜時發現單位內沒有廁紙，故到附近便利店購買，卻發現「原來便利店係冇廁紙賣」，最終搭的士返回官邸，被網民斥她堅離地、缺乏常識。<br />\n<br />\n半夜乘的士回官邸<br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨稱近日突然卸下36年多的官職，不少事也要適應和學習，舉例指由於要搬屋，想盡快回復普通市民身份，故由官邸搬入灣仔服務式住宅會景閣時，至午夜時才發現沒有廁紙，不能入住：「我就走咗去間便利店，諗住去買一、兩卷廁紙，原來便利店係冇廁紙賣，所以又要搭的士喺半夜三更返去政務司司長官邸。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭並解釋為何日前乘搭港鐵不懂用八達通出閘，指極少搭港鐵，在南港島綫入閘時，閘門自動打開，故此出閘時亦以為閘門會自動打開。<br />\n<br />\n本報昨日致電會景閣管理處，管理處的負責人表示，租客可以選擇一個有免費廁紙提供的家務管理服務計劃，另外，租客亦可以致電管理處免費索取廁紙。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民指，便利店沒有廁紙賣是常識，有網民諷指「原來咁打得，做官咁多年，咁叻嘅女人，但唔識搭地鐵，唔識買廁紙&hellip;&hellip;」另有網民質疑她為何不買紙巾解決問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170123/19906008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170123%2F19906008&d=5uNkoBKOFFInbKPjzc0vjYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=0efd6220\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170123%2F19906008&h=1ef54863\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170123/19906008</a>"},{"pid":"452241f582a6e31b49bac4965d3ef89db98a060f","tid":1289232,"uid":242537,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:16:51.000Z","msg":"八達通唔識用 便利店冇廁紙賣 所有人既死都唔關政府事<br />\n月娥鬥賤 你真係no.1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超離地"},{"pid":"29df5b97f83e2a13e0a1db1ef4f1fb7725f7a09b","tid":1289232,"uid":150742,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:19:39.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味扮乜佢自己都係基層中嘅基層"},{"pid":"eaa7cfbaaf8185651a2fe71f36930f4742ea9844","tid":1289232,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"離地娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec940b90ba91a0563c3e34bd8088080467c9ed1","tid":1289232,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"不嬲屎眼係用脷奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廁紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nwhat the fuck is that<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcf2e3a0ea62f05a97047b730cca98362ed446d","tid":1289232,"uid":128369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"係有廁紙賣但唔係間間7仔有<br />\n部分7仔米都有賣"},{"pid":"2dc19be0f0ebac4ea91b993e173164c111e51074","tid":1289232,"uid":62708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:39:37.000Z","msg":"證明高分低能 年年考第一都可以係無常識既"},{"pid":"2b6498d06309a790911f363cbece448c817d3103","tid":1289232,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffcf2e3a0ea62f05a97047b730cca98362ed446d","tid":1289232,"uid":128369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"係有廁紙賣但唔係間間7仔有<br />\n部分7仔米都有賣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁又一證明<br />\n佢揾咗一、兩間就落呢個結論<br />\n真離地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775027637c3b7fded456dce7f895075147374f88","tid":1289232,"uid":2839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"仲有單比$500 個大陸落黎既假乞兒阿婆, 仲要影晒相扮好心, 做過社會福利處處長都唔知呢d 有左十幾廿年既假乞兒, 屌佢老味西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.